videos.headline: Neil Pau'u dives for the pylon for BYU TD
videos.description: Jaren Hall completes a pass to Neil Pau'u who dives for the pylon to score a 4-yard touchdown and give BYU a 10-0 lead over Utah.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Neil Pau'u dives for the pylon for BYU TD) 2021/09/11 ESHEET

videos.headline: Charlie Brewer finds Brant Kuithe for 20-yard Utah TD
videos.description: Charlie Brewer finds Brant Kuithe in the end zone for a 20-yard touchdown for Utah to cut the BYU lead to 10-7.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Brant Kuithe makes 20-yard TD grab for Utah) 2021/09/11 ESHEET

videos.headline: BYU extends their lead with TD before halftime
videos.description: BYU pushes their lead to 16-7 as Jaren Hall finds Samson Nacua for a 2-yard score in the closing moments of the first half.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (BYU extends their lead with TD before halftime) 2021/09/11 ESHEET

videos.headline: Jaren Hall links up with Gunner Romney for a BYU TD
videos.description: Jaren Hall completes a pass to Gunner Romney in the end zone for a 4-yard BYU score.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Jaren Hall links up with Gunner Romney for a BYU TD) 2021/09/11 ESHEET

videos.headline: Micah Bernard evades multiple tackles to score 22-yard Utah TD
videos.description: Micah Bernard takes the handoff and slips through a handful of tackles to reach the end zone and score a 22-yard Utah touchdown.
